{"tid":1812271,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"［學術討論］咩係人身保護令","createTime":"2020-01-05T11:04:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-14T18:38:23.000Z","uid":165869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"4a668d61eb6dbf73ddf685e3c5270fd0e6c32dc9","tid":1812271,"uid":165869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T11:04:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>有冇人可以解答一下申請人身保護令要唔要錢 要幾錢 要點申請 邊個可以申請 去邊到申請<br />\n<br />\n濫捕一次就申請一次 <br />\n我唔想大家坐完48仲要宵禁報到禁足</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n【明報專訊】大批市民於周日參與九龍遊行，後演變為警民衝突。有年輕男子當日下午途經佐敦道期間，在行人路遭防暴警員拘捕，警方其後一直拒絕提供拘捕警員身分，更三度提供不同版本的答案。男子昨向高等法院申請人身保護令，要求警方立即放人。律政司最終到庭表示，事主即將獲釋，案件遂無限期押後，至申請方另有通知為止（sine die）。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/pns/要聞/article/20191022/s00001/1571682415033/問警身分被覆3版本-被捕者申人身保護令\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%E8%A6%81%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20191022%2Fs00001%2F1571682415033%2F%E5%95%8F%E8%AD%A6%E8%BA%AB%E5%88%86%E8%A2%AB%E8%A6%863%E7%89%88%E6%9C%AC-%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95%E8%80%85%E7%94%B3%E4%BA%BA%E8%BA%AB%E4%BF%9D%E8%AD%B7%E4%BB%A4&d=4MF4O%2Bfy8eJNXT4C%2FvKi1bvH1KbbL%2ByyGPsbuV3zdoQ%3D&h=b280e98b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%E8%A6%81%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20191022%2Fs00001%2F1571682415033%2F%E5%95%8F%E8%AD%A6%E8%BA%AB%E5%88%86%E8%A2%AB%E8%A6%863%E7%89%88%E6%9C%AC-%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95%E8%80%85%E7%94%B3%E4%BA%BA%E8%BA%AB%E4%BF%9D%E8%AD%B7%E4%BB%A4&h=316c5878\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/pns/要聞/article/20191022/s00001/1571682415033/問警身分被覆3版本-被捕者申人身保護令</a>"},{"pid":"8fc8fe80db6ddaf6391f3b405368823ef45a8701","tid":1812271,"uid":165869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T11:06:38.000Z","msg":"黑警濫用職權同法律 點解我哋唔善用返法律所賦予嘅權益 就算有少少希望可以早啲出返嚟都好"},{"pid":"8894ea96fc91cdbda621ce8994306ab122688aff","tid":1812271,"uid":310914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T11:08:19.000Z","msg":"Lm學嘢"},{"pid":"cb71c49c64835f0353a13ce54804de487bf75391","tid":1812271,"uid":301666,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T11:20:09.000Z","msg":"人身保護令，即係要求警方將被羈留嘅人，帶到法官面前，由法官判斷係咪非法拘留 (unlawful detention)。<br />\n<br />\n申請程序其實唔難，只需要填form交俾高等法院就得了。唔一定要working hours 之內交表，因為會有法官負責緊急聆訊<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔一定要被捕者本人申請，可以由其他人申請的。但係申請人同被捕者應該要有啲關係 (locus standi)，例如係朋友、屋企人等。"},{"pid":"cff5f915c2919c70d23371ba2831802c06ddb990","tid":1812271,"uid":334720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T11:45:04.000Z","msg":"各位手足，同意與否，請聽我一言，睇哂佢，Spread出去<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1812233/page/1#preview\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1812233/page/1#preview</a><br />\n<br />\n我P牌推唔到 唯有咁樣推比大家睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5cc09a4f67f01e8247a354c324026b2c5f0d6d5","tid":1812271,"uid":1524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T14:42:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7552a7198c97979a13ad835e3599dca216ca7f9","tid":1812271,"uid":6347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T18:38:23.000Z","msg":"推到有攻略<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}